Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經溺過水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不會游泳 也沒辦法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得自己快要不行了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被路過的男孩子救了上來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人就是所謂的「救命恩人」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美櫻的真心英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…其實我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？ 不清楚？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不太記得那時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在我的心裡就是這樣的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對美櫻來說 是很珍貴的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連名字都不曾知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有機會的話真希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他說一聲「謝謝」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 優
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點事想拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}就是美術部的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}愛上了即將畢業的前輩的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}春輝居然會拍戀愛題材 真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們的腳本君說無論如何都想拍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是最後一次了 所以想以高中生活為舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是電影研究部現在這批人所能拍的最後一部電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 希望能把大家想做的事都融匯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 在這部電影中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要美術部的女主角所畫的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幅畫 想拜託你們三位幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 希望選出你們三位的畫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最能表現出電影主旨的一幅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要放暑假了還要給你們添麻煩 非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後選畫的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是導演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝來選…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫的主題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主題自然是「戀愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀…戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛到底是什麼顏色的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到戀愛 果然非粉色莫屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墜入愛河的話整個世界都唰地一下變成粉色的了不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏有過戀愛的經歷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女漫畫裡不都是這種感覺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會是什麼顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得大概是銀色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然閃閃發光的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是放置不管的話就會褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果光線太強的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變得太耀眼讓人無法直視這一點也很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還可以這麼考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直和我的想法一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 我也覺得有點意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼合拍的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為對事物的看法很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.33,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:44.79,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演員的日程安排不要和考試衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話盡量在暑假就拍攝完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的空閒時間 就全都拿來拍個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的夏天可不是一般的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是高中時代最後一個夏天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段回憶居然全都要被社團活動佔據什麼的 也太淒慘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縱享電影 我倒覺得是個不錯的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝是無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正肯定要去和合田約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩個根本沒單獨約過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 誒~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然沒約會過嗎 明明天天放學都一起回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是因為剛好方向一樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝啊春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍電影的時候倒是自信滿滿積極向上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到戀愛的問題上就縮起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少說廢話 快去把劇本改好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保養的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個攝像機是很重要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這是我從秋哥那借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥…就是春輝的哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥也拍電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前稍微拍過一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他特別愛看電影 所以很在行
Comment: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒──
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說之前總是拍不出能讓秋哥滿意的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我一定會用這傢伙拍個好電影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候好讓秋哥大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們關係真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假妳有什麼安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是備考生 果然要準備考試什麼的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 明明妳這麼忙還要拜託妳幫我們畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 春輝你有什麼安排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概要拍片子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想盡可能趁著暑假多拍一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅 黃 橙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到戀愛 果然應該是粉色？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 這樣就和小夏的想法一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 戀愛真的可以用色彩表現出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要幫上春輝的忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要讓春輝 選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里應該已經開始畫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定畫得很順利吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然比不上她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 不可以說喪氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週的煙花大會大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也包括春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和春輝一起看煙花…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻說她也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻這丫頭真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說什麼沒和春輝在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看都是兩情相悅啊 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幫他們撮合一下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在學習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 煙花 當然優也要一起去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡去那種人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去找個別人一起好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧 和那個人一起玩個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…果然聽起來還挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不定也挺想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這麼定了 我得趕快去準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習加油哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝會說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能覺得我可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到盂蘭盆節過後…一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和救了美櫻的人打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方聯繫過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說「差不多應該可以了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有沒有忘帶什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 甚平的優點就是穿起來簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優也穿一次就知…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:36.86,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什你們兩個會一起過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好在那邊碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 要和之前說的恩人見面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等盂蘭盆節之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會是個什麼樣的人呢 我好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小夏這麼期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳想啊 這展開多有戲劇性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方能夠見到美櫻也一定很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會嗎…真是那樣的話就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是理所當然的嘛 我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 張嘴~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻不是喜歡這些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 優他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 沒接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留言也沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 我們兩個人去轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣氛不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣給我變成情侶吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有小夏的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 燈里里真可愛 小天使~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 要不要去搭個話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太慫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒──但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我請妳吃點什麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃法蘭克福香腸 烤魷魚 黃油馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有巧克力香蕉 蘋果糖 棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這是要把我吃破產嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然不管你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不要緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有點熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻 美櫻！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了點冷飲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…明明馬上就要放煙花了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在意 正好我也想休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳剛才和夏樹提到過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前啊 我受到過一個人的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想著要去和他道謝 但是一直沒有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次終於可以見到那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人…是男的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 玉屋是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳都不知道是什麼就在那喊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易來看一次煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人看也沒什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫的進展怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…對不起 還在苦惱中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻不是說過不喜歡站在鏡頭前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是畫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是電影部最後的一部作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是集大成作吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 想讓美櫻也能參與進來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛的顏色 或許並不只有一種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進展不順利的時候 就會像昏暗的夜色一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只因為一些小事 就會心神蕩漾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後誕生出各種顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個世界也變得繽紛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是 煙花一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10厘米…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能比10厘米更近的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去買點吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛的畫 我好像知道該怎麼畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我的人 是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顧危險去救一個素不相識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是件簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要好好向他道謝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我拿著花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了美櫻的那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就安眠在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…
